PRIVACY POLICY for ibis Paint in the United States of America
Last updated: October 31, 2024
We, IBIS INC., respect your privacy. As we operate our website and provide you with our services, we process personal data about you in accordance with applicable data protection laws, including the amendments to the California Consumer Privacy Act (the "CCPA") adopted pursuant to the California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA) and the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act of the United States of America (the "COPPA").
This is our privacy policy for residents in the U.S.A. on how we process and protect your personal data who use our "ibis Paint". We may revise this privacy policy from time to time. You can obtain the latest version of this policy on our site.
This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect personally identifiable information of U.S.A. residents and any information related to it ("personal information") and non-personal information on this site.
Please refer to the ‚Äú
PRIVACY POLICY for ibis Paint in the EEA / the UK
