AppLovin Array Terms of Service
APPLOVIN PLATFORM DATA PROCESSING AGREEMENT
AppLovin Demand Partner¬†Data Processing Agreement
Effective Date
: October 30, 2024
You can find the prior version
here
.
AppLovin Corporation (‚Äúwe,‚Äù ‚Äúus,‚Äù ‚Äúour,‚Äù or ‚ÄúAppLovin‚Äù) operates a suite of tools for app developers and other businesses to automate and optimize the marketing and monetization of their platforms, products, or services by enabling the placement of different types of advertisements on digital properties including mobile apps, websites, and connected TV devices (collectively, the ‚ÄúAdvertising Services‚Äù or ‚ÄúServices‚Äù).¬† As explained below, consumers interact with us in a few ways, primarily through advertisements served by AppLovin on behalf of advertisers.
The AppLovin Privacy Policy (this ‚ÄúPrivacy Policy‚Äù) explains how we collect, use, and share information through our Services and advertising platform, and our corporate website at www.applovin.com (the ‚ÄúWebsite‚Äù), as well as your choices related to that information.
Contents
Our Advertising Services
Our Website
Additional Provisions for EU/UK/Swiss Individuals
U.S. Multistate Privacy Notice
